resources.residEmptySourceMessage_GenericDevice:
Aikace-aikacen Hotuna yana nuna maka hotuna da kuma bidiyoyi daga duk naúrorinka a cikin wuri guda.

Don ganin ƙunshiya daga wasu naúrori tafi SkyDrive.com/windowsdon zazzagewa da kuma girka Kwafin Gwaji na Microsoft SkyDrive a kansu. Sannan kuma, shiga tare da asusunka na Microsoft ka kuma tabbata an Samar da fayiloli a kan wannan kwamfuta gare ni a kan sauran naúrorian zaɓi akwatin zaɓi.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_Device: Idan kana da wani, ka tabbata ka saka su a cikin laburarin Hotunanka {{%1}}.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_Service: Ƙara wasu hotuna zuwa asusunka don farawa.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_SkyDrive:
SkyDrive yana ba ka maájiyar kan layi kyauta don hotuna, bidiyoyi da kuma daftarai saboda ka sami dama gare su daga koína.

Tafi zuwa SkyDrive.com don farawa. Za a nuna duk wasu hotuna da bidiyoyi da ka adana a nan.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_PicturesLibrary:
Don farawa, haɗa wata naúra (kamara , waya, USB filash diraib da sauransu), ka kuma shigo ko kwafin hotuna da da bidiyoyi a cikin maádanar Hotunanka.

Idan tuni ka na da hotuna ko bidiyoyi a kan wannan kwamfuta, ka tabbata suna a cikin laburarinka na Hotuna. Za ka iya gudanar da laburaren Hotunanka daga File Explorer.
